  "texts": [
    "LLMs for title and abstract screeningBy creating structured prompts with clear instructions, an LLM can feasibly be used for evaluating the relevance of a scientific publication.",
    "In comparison to some other solutions, the LLM-based screening may have some advantages.",
    "On the one hand, the flexible nature of the approach allows adaptation to a specific subject.",
    "Depending on the question, different prompts for relevant criteria and instructions can be used to address the individual research question.",
    "On the other hand, the approach can create reproducible results, given a fixed model, parameters, prompting strategy, and defined threshold."
